Title : 2003–04 Ivy League men's basketball season
Text : The '''2003–04 Ivy League men's basketball season''' was the [[Ivy League]]'s 50th season of basketball. The team with the best record (Princeton Tigers) played in the [[2004 NCAA Men's Division I Basketball Tournament]]. Jason Forte, a junior point guard from the Brown Bears, was awarded the [[Ivy League Men's Basketball Player of the Year]].

